snippet.title: Lysfangha – Introduction – A Miracle of Light
snippet.description:
Embody the demi-goddess Imë and purify the temple where the Lysfangha is kept. Using your temporal powers, duplicate yourself by going back in time. Cooperate with your clones to repel the invasion!

Art: Félix Donadio & Jeanne Plounevez

Composer: Clément Gaunard
https://clementgaunard.wixsite.com/sound-designer

Narrator: Kevin England
https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevinenglandsound/

Subscribe to our channel – https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnrY8mIKE9f1dJfuGYhv3Sg?sub_confirmation=1
Check our social networks – https://linktr.ee/Lysfangha
